<body>
    <h1>T7 - Technical Document</h1>
    <div class=3D"Section1">
        <p local-id=3D"21817ab69514"></p>
<h1 local-id=3D"8a6c920a1600" id=3D"T7-TechnicalDocument-1.Introduction">1.=
 Introduction</h1>
<h2 local-id=3D"085354736c03" id=3D"T7-TechnicalDocument-1.1Purpose">1.1 Pu=
rpose</h2>
<p local-id=3D"7ddaee76eb82">This document explains the complete implementa=
tion of a monitoring solution that:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"dcaa6c3b843e">
<li local-id=3D"bdc144759e41">
<p local-id=3D"442183056d6d">Counts files in a system temp directory</p></l=
i>
<li local-id=3D"ffbd851cfc91">
<p local-id=3D"d330d5436f02">Pushes the metric to Prometheus Pushgateway</p=
></li>
<li local-id=3D"326b8f1282f6">
<p local-id=3D"5cf1dd9162f4">Visualizes the metric in Grafana</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"64fb3dcce0ae">
<p local-id=3D"8811aa2213ff">Sends alert notifications when file count exce=
eds threshold</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"2223a66ca7c7">
<p local-id=3D"4c15c5cf477b">Runs on both Lambda (container-based) and ECS =
Fargate</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"a756b72a15d4">Intended audience:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"88b7dd132c69">
<li local-id=3D"3b6747e52759">
<p local-id=3D"971d4cb1a848">CTO</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"7b7367f94113">
<p local-id=3D"12591de9e26e">Solution Architects</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"d2bccefc6b85">
<p local-id=3D"a1626f942bcd">DevOps Engineers</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"cc54a22aeb61">
<p local-id=3D"82fa03e985ab">Developers</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"c3e3d67c2af5">This document is written so that a reader can =
independently implement the entire solution.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"c8b4e4ab01d2">
<h2 local-id=3D"ad309809fe3c" id=3D"T7-TechnicalDocument-1.2Scope">1.2 Scop=
e</h2>
<p local-id=3D"aaa7f3ca6f23">This document covers:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"ab10cd9b3c07">
<li local-id=3D"8d0661acbda4">
<p local-id=3D"24de41689c2e">Collector implementation</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"c5d239a0c8e9">
<p local-id=3D"7b6d1363a109">Scheduling</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"a72f074cd1da">
<p local-id=3D"8ab37bc39d14">Metric push mechanism</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"3947822b7c4e">
<p local-id=3D"01632e07f8c2">Grafana dashboard creation</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"6faf873c18c2">
<p local-id=3D"5ee1923987d5">Alert configuration</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"b738b9cdde63">
<p local-id=3D"31a367cd6fe1">Containerization</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"cfd130acdbb5">
<p local-id=3D"de1f8674b679">Deployment on Lambda &amp; ECS Fargate</p></li=
>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"60943fa15790">Out of scope:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"c80e55d9b854">
<li local-id=3D"117e1c4fc070">
<p local-id=3D"19a35de577df">Infrastructure provisioning via Terraform (man=
ual console steps described)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"61d64d865f68">
<p local-id=3D"0b431bb15048">Enterprise-level scaling configurations</p></l=
i>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"0f91f15bb4b7">
<h1 local-id=3D"042ccc7358a3" id=3D"T7-TechnicalDocument-2.OverviewoftheDev=
OpsProject">2. Overview of the DevOps Project</h1>
<h2 local-id=3D"ca46bb025eea" id=3D"T7-TechnicalDocument-2.1Definition">2.1=
 Definition</h2>
<p local-id=3D"af00f4f787e2">This project implements a monitoring pipeline =
using modern DevOps principles:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"e5c5041249f8">
<li local-id=3D"964bbe723a19">
<p local-id=3D"1b08b4433154">Automated metric collection</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"fa4dfd7ac3e0">
<p local-id=3D"cb0b79ebb38c">Scheduled execution</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"0f62310ffe13">
<p local-id=3D"ef984da6f41d">Centralized metric storage</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"46cd07f34f3d">
<p local-id=3D"35f44297f171">Visualization</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"86c1b70199ad">
<p local-id=3D"6e0a1c755002">Alerting</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"066741aa6439">
<p local-id=3D"519b9c3cb541">Container portability</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"b9623f2cecc0">Benefits:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"34fec04bda9a">
<li local-id=3D"764a099481cb">
<p local-id=3D"c50d14aaab18">Automated monitoring</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"2a9b4eab6b4c">
<p local-id=3D"5edb37f24fab">Real-time visibility</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"80425372522a">
<p local-id=3D"42b3b6534d5f">Proactive alerting</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"27c29fe8d2c3">
<p local-id=3D"01a9e4b51f19">Cloud-native scalability</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"5bb890182889">
<h2 local-id=3D"65e03b3a5c4a" id=3D"T7-TechnicalDocument-2.2AWSWell-Archite=
ctedFrameworkAlignment">2.2 AWS Well-Architected Framework Alignment</h2>
<h3 local-id=3D"0eb69179a3ee" id=3D"T7-TechnicalDocument-1.OperationalExcel=
lence">1. Operational Excellence</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"db2f692e59a6">
<li local-id=3D"f179373e6ac8">
<p local-id=3D"26b783b0625d">Automated execution using EventBridge</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"491dc2a43ef0">
<p local-id=3D"fd2fd9f89751">CloudWatch logging enabled</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"0d062bd0d674">
<p local-id=3D"2aca9c3ecbbe">Reproducible container deployment</p></li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"ef9b6dd1e2e9" id=3D"T7-TechnicalDocument-2.Security">2. Sec=
urity</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"1483a45134cc">
<li local-id=3D"91af87d3debe">
<p local-id=3D"18e0627d0c20">IAM roles with least privilege</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"1f2cf57d7200">
<p local-id=3D"bf34c0e5fd85">No hardcoded credentials</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"8f83d95057ff">
<p local-id=3D"0b8657c95980">Environment variables for configuration</p></l=
i>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"bb86fd5c8392" id=3D"T7-TechnicalDocument-3.Reliability">3. =
Reliability</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"67f7b0f7243b">
<li local-id=3D"9b229bc25e84">
<p local-id=3D"25aef2d89b63">Scheduled execution every 5 minutes</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"9f4efeb15398">
<p local-id=3D"1203d35817db">Alert if metric crosses threshold</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"5622aa0bbbd0">
<p local-id=3D"02f66612c3c5">Logs for failure detection</p></li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"5066c3099c1e" id=3D"T7-TechnicalDocument-4.PerformanceEffic=
iency">4. Performance Efficiency</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"50569ca85938">
<li local-id=3D"ada07f76a263">
<p local-id=3D"e87b50ebe684">Lightweight collector</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"23dd9f35247f">
<p local-id=3D"4c9e58820d8a">Minimal runtime footprint</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"25fb8b00cd7e">
<p local-id=3D"6b27934a8b0b">Serverless compute</p></li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"deaefbd4d67f" id=3D"T7-TechnicalDocument-5.CostOptimization=
">5. Cost Optimization</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"992b7dcf632a">
<li local-id=3D"4fab36eed353">
<p local-id=3D"9a6be2df1056">Lambda pay-per-use</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"a71b6cc987c5">
<p local-id=3D"e0d14b006b77">ECS scheduled task (no always-on cost)</p></li=
>
<li local-id=3D"2ce7221ad5c9">
<p local-id=3D"0d134cf6a3d6">Small container image</p></li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"c5953d293098" id=3D"T7-TechnicalDocument-6.Sustainability">=
6. Sustainability</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"6e18b8bab40a">
<li local-id=3D"edff6ea37259">
<p local-id=3D"82c28ef956af">Event-driven execution</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"6ae5bb792ac6">
<p local-id=3D"eb727f02bc2d">No idle infrastructure</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"11301bca2a10">
<h2 local-id=3D"caf8c1b88f2e" id=3D"T7-TechnicalDocument-2.3GoalsandObjecti=
ves">2.3 Goals and Objectives</h2>
<ul local-id=3D"2effbc1161e9">
<li local-id=3D"28dca5539839">
<p local-id=3D"413d4596d0b7">Automate temp directory monitoring</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"ae3d3be8dfef">
<p local-id=3D"18982e324733">Visualize historical trends</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"ababb9cd2f91">
<p local-id=3D"2c56820495ab">Trigger alert when count &gt; 100</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"d01ad8bd6091">
<p local-id=3D"05c3a463b736">Deploy same collector in Lambda and ECS</p></l=
i>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"23f311bd4b80">
<h2 local-id=3D"22575adc8e07" id=3D"T7-TechnicalDocument-2.4ConstraintsandA=
ssumptions">2.4 Constraints and Assumptions</h2>
<p local-id=3D"443f834ac25c">Constraints:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"3baf98085a21">
<li local-id=3D"84fd4f119711">
<p local-id=3D"df60222b0832">Limited budget</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"4424dcb35385">
<p local-id=3D"0bca0b56fbc1">Small-scale environment</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"c61745b1f5b9">
<p local-id=3D"527fbc6b2352">Single Pushgateway endpoint</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"0d87ed34bd9a">Assumptions:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"364f4ce6c530">
<li local-id=3D"aed9df1f61ed">
<p local-id=3D"c154385c017f">Pushgateway reachable from AWS</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"468ff5893197">
<p local-id=3D"36ac158883fa">Prometheus scraping Pushgateway</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"ea8929ac63ae">
<p local-id=3D"1b2dba6d0e64">Grafana configured with Prometheus data source=
</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"a49ed6e3a908">
<h1 local-id=3D"6606d153c66f" id=3D"T7-TechnicalDocument-3.ArchitectureandI=
nfrastructure">3. Architecture and Infrastructure</h1>
<h2 local-id=3D"74a404e47aab" id=3D"T7-TechnicalDocument-3.1InfrastructureO=
verview">3.1 Infrastructure Overview</h2>
<p local-id=3D"2aec95fcab98">Architecture Flow:</p>
<p local-id=3D"b29592051598">EventBridge (5 min schedule)<br>
=E2=86=92 Lambda or ECS<br>
=E2=86=92 SSM (executes file count command)<br>
=E2=86=92 Pushgateway (HTTP push)<br>
=E2=86=92 Prometheus (scrapes metrics)<br>
=E2=86=92 Grafana (visualization)<br>
=E2=86=92 Telegram alert (notification)</p>
<p local-id=3D"60b0f96746bd"></p><span class=3D"confluence-embedded-file-wr=
apper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size"><img class=3D"c=
onfluence-embedded-image image-center" alt=3D"diagram-export-3-10-2026-11_1=
2_55-PM-20260310-174407.png" width=3D"468" loading=3D"lazy" src=3D"20e401c7=
59046ff4db194837cf849e226318621b40c748adc98920fe1e8bd8f9" data-image-src=3D=
"https://iamops.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1804533771/diagram-=
export-3-10-2026-11_12_55-PM-20260310-174407.png?version=3D1&amp;modificati=
onDate=3D1773164656227&amp;cacheVersion=3D1&amp;api=3Dv2" data-height=3D"94=
5" data-width=3D"1730" data-unresolved-comment-count=3D"0" data-linked-reso=
urce-id=3D"1849622549" data-linked-resource-version=3D"1" data-linked-resou=
rce-type=3D"attachment" data-linked-resource-default-alias=3D"diagram-expor=
t-3-10-2026-11_12_55-PM-20260310-174407.png" data-base-url=3D"https://iamop=
s.atlassian.net/wiki" data-linked-resource-content-type=3D"image/png" data-=
linked-resource-container-id=3D"1804533771" data-linked-resource-container-=
version=3D"4" data-media-id=3D"3ab54fc2-4b83-48af-9e8a-b18c81baf581" data-m=
edia-type=3D"file" height=3D"255"></span>
<hr local-id=3D"ed563210ef51">
<h2 local-id=3D"1ca93724aaf7" id=3D"T7-TechnicalDocument-3.2Environments">3=
.2 Environments</h2>
<ul local-id=3D"606cc0431621">
<li local-id=3D"6f5830e7e8cb">
<p local-id=3D"bdcbcf4e8931">Development: Local testing of container</p></l=
i>
<li local-id=3D"614391325866">
<p local-id=3D"e3037ba5b26d">Production: AWS Lambda &amp; ECS</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"ba155d91785d">
<p local-id=3D"e94ed136f7c6">Monitoring: Grafana Cloud</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"a993d1d55731">
<h2 local-id=3D"27c56144ab29" id=3D"T7-TechnicalDocument-3.3ToolsandTechnol=
ogies">3.3 Tools and Technologies</h2>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-table-width=3D"1800" data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"6=
3f044f7-b2c7-4b91-b580-acc769e56f14" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>
<tr data-local-id=3D"d3101538ccbf">
<th data-local-id=3D"6980db542e1c" class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p local-id=3D"07e1d533cadb">Component</p></th>
<th data-local-id=3D"50bd490c7c28" class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p local-id=3D"f890653b432b">Tool</p></th>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"1fe64275070d">
<td data-local-id=3D"3f7a5776095b" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"f43bbbdc0325">Compute</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"9c4ee87b7733" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"fde2dd4dd9a9">AWS Lambda</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"224ac48693ad">
<td data-local-id=3D"2786f5297f8d" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"63bc5d609e16">Container Runtime</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"2adac5e08a0d" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"74b76091c0e5">AWS ECS Fargate</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"872a3b26df1a">
<td data-local-id=3D"01feaa0173e0" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"54eb50dbf346">Scheduler</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"a64183b45dfd" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"85e1587838b4">EventBridge</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"ac5df81eef82">
<td data-local-id=3D"5640cc31c061" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"4a33eb37fe97">Metrics Push</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"160abbcf540c" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"652097dac672">Prometheus Pushgateway</p></td>
</tr>
