<hr local-id=3D"737f3e7184a4">
<h1 local-id=3D"9a13f9e77398" id=3D"T7-TechnicalDocument-4.Implementation">=
4. Implementation</h1>
<hr local-id=3D"1242725e6d33">
<h1 local-id=3D"444479f4b104" id=3D"T7-TechnicalDocument-Part1=E2=80=94Buil=
dCollector(CoreImplementation)">Part 1 =E2=80=94 Build Collector (Core Impl=
ementation)</h1>
<h2 local-id=3D"d90743525d1e" id=3D"T7-TechnicalDocument-4.1PythonCollector=
Code(ZIP-BasedLambdaImplementation)">4.1 Python Collector Code (ZIP-Based L=
ambda Implementation)</h2>
<p local-id=3D"88f4513b34f7">Initially, the collector was implemented using=
 a standard AWS Lambda (ZIP deployment model).</p>
<p local-id=3D"c865e8d60d39">The function performs the following operations=
:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"dc8a31b826bf">
<li local-id=3D"9112d24b5488">
<p local-id=3D"a7f1e3239dbe">Uses AWS SSM to remotely execute a shell comma=
nd on EC2</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"181de191b03e">
<p local-id=3D"173b850dccfe">Counts the number of files in the configured t=
emp directory</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"6127018ec698">
<p local-id=3D"2ec492296e2a">Pushes the metric to Prometheus Pushgateway</p=
></li>
<li local-id=3D"6462f764a076">
<p local-id=3D"747c37ad7070">Logs execution details to CloudWatch</p></li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"480953043a5b" id=3D"T7-TechnicalDocument-EnvironmentVariabl=
esUsed">Environment Variables Used</h3>
<p local-id=3D"f10568252502">The following environment variables were confi=
gured in Lambda:</p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">PUSHGAT=
EWAY_URL
EC2_INSTANCE_ID
TEMP_DIR_PATH
METRIC_JOB_NAME
ENVIRONMENT
SSM_TIMEOUT_SECONDS</pre>
</div>
</div>
<h3 local-id=3D"2713b340dd3e" id=3D"T7-TechnicalDocument-MetricFormat">Metr=
ic Format</h3>
<p local-id=3D"8cb56519091d">The metric pushed to Pushgateway:</p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">temp_di=
r_file_count{environment=3D"prod",host=3D"ec2-main",path=3D"/tmp"} &lt;valu=
e&gt;</pre>
</div>
</div>
<p local-id=3D"7ab41c85ac44">This implementation validated:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"252134506861">
<li local-id=3D"4b67bc5eb9bd">
<p local-id=3D"e41c4c7ec7bb">SSM execution flow</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"0e7b25e65da5">
<p local-id=3D"774d816515e3">Pushgateway connectivity</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"0b4d4112bfa7">
<p local-id=3D"9a59d650fef2">Prometheus scraping</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"532b9e42f57e">
<p local-id=3D"bf85e3f9e800">Grafana dashboard functionality</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"badbfc407fb4">
<p local-id=3D"2aefce087050">Alert triggering mechanism</p></li>
</ul>
