<hr local-id=3D"51e94212901c">
<h1 local-id=3D"0fcd4c45d59d" id=3D"T7-TechnicalDocument-=F0=9F=94=B9Part2=
=E2=80=94Container-BasedLambdaDeployment(Bonus)">=F0=9F=94=B9 Part 2 =E2=80=
=94 Container-Based Lambda Deployment (Bonus)</h1>
<p local-id=3D"1c2c2f9c6138">After validating the collector logic using ZIP=
 deployment, the solution was enhanced to use container-based Lambda for po=
rtability and production readiness.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"4ced4d416362">
<h2 local-id=3D"f83748b43741" id=3D"T7-TechnicalDocument-5.1CreateContainer=
Image">5.1 Create Container Image</h2>
<p local-id=3D"42f7f1a9eece">Dockerfile:</p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">FROM pu=
blic.ecr.aws/lambda/python:3.11

COPY requirements.txt .
RUN pip install -r requirements.txt --target "${LAMBDA_TASK_ROOT}"

COPY app.py ${LAMBDA_TASK_ROOT}

CMD ["app.lambda_handler"]</pre>
</div>
</div>
<p local-id=3D"11fcfa2026ba">This ensures:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"1ebbf255cc26">
<li local-id=3D"e5d026c3e37c">
<p local-id=3D"6f29b2c10a6b">Consistent runtime</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"b2de3e7e2220">
<p local-id=3D"9ddd5037c2d7">Dependency packaging</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"e36769836399">
<p local-id=3D"1baa14718286">Deployment portability</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"0a4c7572968e">
<h2 local-id=3D"aaec7cdd4607" id=3D"T7-TechnicalDocument-5.2BuildandPushIma=
getoECR">5.2 Build and Push Image to ECR</h2>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">docker =
build -t tempdir-collector .
docker tag tempdir-collector &lt;account&gt;.dkr.ecr.&lt;region&gt;.amazona=
ws.com/tempdir-collector:latest
docker push &lt;repo-url&gt;</pre>
</div>
</div>
