<h2 local-id=3D"17bb4063940b" id=3D"T7-TechnicalDocument-5.3DeployLambda(Co=
ntainer-Based)">5.3 Deploy Lambda (Container-Based)</h2>
<p local-id=3D"bd17cde48248">Steps performed:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"4f2c658959c2">
<li local-id=3D"6fbb34b08ea6">
