<hr local-id=3D"23dbf9b1b843">
<h1 local-id=3D"610b8fa546a1" id=3D"T7-TechnicalDocument-=F0=9F=94=B9Part3=
=E2=80=94LambdaScheduling">=F0=9F=94=B9 Part 3 =E2=80=94 Lambda Scheduling<=
/h1>
<p local-id=3D"99353be8327a">Both ZIP-based and container-based Lambda vers=
ions were scheduled using EventBridge.</p>
<p local-id=3D"8f2ba109f7f9">Schedule configuration:</p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">rate(5 =
minutes)</pre>
</div>
</div>
<p local-id=3D"f1cfbec3b216">Target:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"7a657e0b127e">
<li local-id=3D"9e1030f73c42">
<p local-id=3D"94e421592641">Lambda function</p></li>
</ul>
