<hr local-id=3D"194a97c5204c">
<h1 local-id=3D"e0f75a5e944a" id=3D"T7-TechnicalDocument-=F0=9F=94=B9Part4=
=E2=80=94ECSDeployment(Bonus)">=F0=9F=94=B9 Part 4 =E2=80=94 ECS Deployment=
 (Bonus)</h1>
<p local-id=3D"c79184b19cb5">The same container image was deployed to ECS F=
argate to demonstrate portability.</p>
