r_file_count &gt; 100</pre>
</div>
</div>
<p local-id=3D"521b9720d40f">Evaluation:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"d7fcc7f6e60f">
<li local-id=3D"5c222f1c2d74">
<p local-id=3D"f9116eaedd11">Every 1 minute</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"82c1aa09bbe0">
<p local-id=3D"be3d4f7accd8">For 5 minutes</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"ec6b4b2b06f6">Contact point:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"8242969917ac">
<li local-id=3D"d48ad033c60d">
<p local-id=3D"66ba2346c94e">Telegram bot</p></li>
</ul><span class=3D"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper c=
