-4f01-876f-06bb7bb2bb17" data-media-type=3D"file" height=3D"991"></span>
<p local-id=3D"21730cda446b"></p>
<p local-id=3D"d6970de5d449">Alert message includes:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"1b47396f942b">
<li local-id=3D"dc7c76ab0ba7">
<p local-id=3D"dd1bd72293c9">Directory path</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"1fb7c959d156">
<p local-id=3D"2f99a74fed47">Current count</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"ceabade7b6cf">
<p local-id=3D"3493eba0a8ea">Timestamp</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"476df53039f3">
<p local-id=3D"9966b60b410e">Host label</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"6a0f3e12ab71">
<h1 local-id=3D"4e51cc671d89" id=3D"T7-TechnicalDocument-8.Monitoring&amp;I=
ncidentManagement">8. Monitoring &amp; Incident Management</h1>
<p local-id=3D"4dd501e3dae4">If alert triggers:</p>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"b425d35f767d">
<li local-id=3D"c7774940d039">
<p local-id=3D"13cc454fc0f3">Investigate CloudWatch logs</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"b8ef542967d8">
<p local-id=3D"42c1402fa657">Check temp directory</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"7a74dc6d2c52">
<p local-id=3D"2e082a22c47b">Clear unnecessary files</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"532681153256">
<p local-id=3D"307e1f994fce">Verify metric returns to normal</p></li>
</ol>
<hr local-id=3D"69297d5a078a">
<h1 local-id=3D"9d4568cd50cc" id=3D"T7-TechnicalDocument-9.CostOptimization=
">9. Cost Optimization</h1>
<p local-id=3D"bcbc6396242e">Lambda:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"2fdc1d98d00d">
<li local-id=3D"05fcb0d326a6">
<p local-id=3D"f9d21afdc85f">Pay per execution</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"fcfa3029af94">
<p local-id=3D"09f416a7243e">Minimal cost</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"65c5fb568618">ECS Scheduled:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"0f9564ec50ed">
<li local-id=3D"cfe84d5e8900">
<p local-id=3D"cdf3714093eb">Runs only when triggered</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"a50798c7215f">
<p local-id=3D"b1a140ea97dc">No idle charges</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"8870f4ed49da">Avoided:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"6122dbcf0b1e">
<li local-id=3D"7bce21bcec06">
<p local-id=3D"414ea1eb367b">Always-on EC2</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"f9bb3eb23b57">
<p local-id=3D"5c7754e869a8">Persistent containers</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"07025e152400">
<h1 local-id=3D"6d98daaa1f5f" id=3D"T7-TechnicalDocument-10.ImplementationT=
imeline">10. Implementation Timeline</h1>
<p local-id=3D"9dad664ef115">Phase 1: Collector development (1 day)<br>
 Phase 2: Lambda deployment (1 day)<br>
 Phase 3: Grafana dashboard &amp; alerts (1 day)<br>
 Phase 4: Containerization &amp; ECS (1 day)</p>
<hr local-id=3D"4614af931bbf">
<h1 local-id=3D"9fbdc3028c75" id=3D"T7-TechnicalDocument-11.ContinuousImpro=
vement">11. Continuous Improvement</h1>
<p local-id=3D"e39b9fb3d15f">Future improvements:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"a39a086629f6">
<li local-id=3D"2b51cf9aa39f">
<p local-id=3D"e22d78f74717">Multi-directory support</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"f41aaa08838a">
<p local-id=3D"6efaa6a14718">Multi-host aggregation</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"fab144059c58">
<p local-id=3D"134cb96fa8ea">Prometheus remote write</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"8ae63249282b">
<p local-id=3D"214a2dc875ac">Slack + Email alert integration</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"b2efefc48418">
<p local-id=3D"4016991deaed">Infrastructure as Code (Terraform)</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"fb0bf224f93e">
<h1 local-id=3D"e85b0d8524b0" id=3D"T7-TechnicalDocument-12.Conclusion">12.=
 Conclusion</h1>
<p local-id=3D"98877ab9ae5f">This solution demonstrates:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"c7428cb01a84">
<li local-id=3D"df440a2c00ed">
<p local-id=3D"e36515d57463">Serverless monitoring</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"5ddc667eed02">
<p local-id=3D"4d1593493f9f">Metric standardization</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"6610cb50a479">
<p local-id=3D"114f419acd41">Cloud-native alerting</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"9bce3b734d3a">
<p local-id=3D"00e6352fdcea">Container portability</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"f7558ffc5570">
<p local-id=3D"985ecf3a30c8">DevOps automation best practices</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"53bcef781c48">The system is scalable, cost-efficient, and pr=
oduction-ready.</p>
    </div>
</body>
